[SPEAKER_00] jer sam htio zaštititi svoje obitelj.

663
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Htio sam zaštititi Sina Božjega.

664
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

665
00:37:44,659 --> 00:37:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije.

666
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] Svjestan svega.

667
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

668
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] htio bi da se stavite

669
00:37:49,599 --> 00:37:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] u Josipovu kožu.

670
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Neko nas bi vjerojatno

671
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] tak i napravio.

672
00:37:52,659 --> 00:37:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj malo.

673
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj,

674
00:37:53,739 --> 00:37:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je sad tu mač.

675
00:37:54,559 --> 00:37:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

676
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

677
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

678
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] Malo moram dramatizirati.

679
00:37:59,559 --> 00:38:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] Deset je.

680
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da ste budni.

681
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

682
00:38:03,059 --> 00:38:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] Polako će oni sad,

683
00:38:04,239 --> 00:38:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] bez brige.

684
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] Lijemo vidjeti

685
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] kada se vraća u Nazaret.

686
00:38:10,099 --> 00:38:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] Saznavši da Arhelaj,

687
00:38:11,739 --> 00:38:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] Arhelaj je jedini preostali Herodov sin

688
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg nije ubio,

689
00:38:15,639 --> 00:38:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] a zašto?

690
00:38:16,039 --> 00:38:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je bio gori od Heroda.

691
00:38:17,260 --> 00:38:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Bio gori od svog starog.

692
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] Arhelaj vlada

693
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] judejom,

694
00:38:23,679 --> 00:38:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] najmijesno svoga oca Heroda,

695
00:38:25,019 --> 00:38:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] bojao se poći onobo,

696
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:27,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa upuće na snu,

697
00:38:27,179 --> 00:38:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] ode u kraj Galilejski,

698
00:38:29,179 --> 00:38:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] u Nazaret.

699
00:38:30,159 --> 00:38:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] U grad koji uopće

700
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] nitko nikad nije skoro čuo.

701
00:38:34,679 --> 00:38:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] U starom zavitu se nikada

702
00:38:36,179 --> 00:38:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] ne spominje Nazaret.

703
00:38:37,059 --> 00:38:38,360
[SPEAKER_00] Neva ga, uopće.

704
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi svi ostali Jeruzalem,

705
00:38:39,619 --> 00:38:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Betlehem,

706
00:38:40,199 --> 00:38:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] to se sve spominje.

707
00:38:41,099 --> 00:38:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nazaret, ne.

708
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, sad tu isto poniznost.

709
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nekoj najveću zavit.

710
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kraj koji su isto židovi mrzili.

711
00:38:49,099 --> 00:38:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se,

712
00:38:50,219 --> 00:38:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] može li što dobro ga izaći iz Nazareta.

713
00:38:52,139 --> 00:38:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite tu isto Josipovu poniznost.

714
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] E sada, ovdje nastaje jedan problem.

715
00:38:57,159 --> 00:39:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se nigdje ne spominje Nazaret,

716
00:39:00,159 --> 00:39:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] a ovdje se kaže,

717
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se ispunile riječi proroka,

718
00:39:03,260 --> 00:39:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] zvaće se Nazarečanin.

719
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] Koji prorok i gdje se to u starom zavitu spominje?

720
00:39:07,559 --> 00:39:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nigdje.

721
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nigdje se ne spominje.

722
00:39:12,019 --> 00:39:14,280
[SPEAKER_00] U čemu je ovdje zapravo riječ?

723
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

724
00:39:15,599 --> 00:39:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] aluzija na Izaiju 11.

725
00:39:18,739 --> 00:39:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] Izaija 11,

726
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] ono što isto u Božiću zapravo čitamo,

727
00:39:22,019 --> 00:39:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] kaže ovo.

728
00:39:23,199 --> 00:39:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, samo na početku.

729
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] Isklijaće mladica iz Spanja Iševa.

730
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:32,219
[SPEAKER_00] Išaj je praotac svih iz Davidove loze,

731
00:39:32,219 --> 00:39:33,719
[SPEAKER_00] zato što je Davidov otac Išaj.

732
00:39:33,719 --> 00:39:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se.

733
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] Izdanak će izbiti iz njegova korijena.

734
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] Izdanak.

735
00:39:37,639 --> 00:39:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se hebriski kaže izdanak,

736
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] kaže se nedzer.

737
00:39:41,460 --> 00:39:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo je zanimljivo zapravo.

738
00:39:43,659 --> 00:39:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Nazaret znači,

739
00:39:45,139 --> 00:39:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] izdanak misli se grana.

740
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi su preveli izdanak.

741
00:39:48,019 --> 00:39:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo znači grana.

742
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] Grana će isklijati iz tog panja Iševa.

743
00:39:51,860 --> 00:39:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo, grad granja.

744
00:39:54,679 --> 00:39:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo je to tako reći.

745
00:39:55,340 --> 00:39:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] Zamišljam, Nazaret, kolu u vestrnima,

746
00:39:57,500 --> 00:40:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] nema nikoga i onda ono granje,

747
00:40:00,219 --> 00:40:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] ide samo.

748
00:40:01,599 --> 00:40:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] To je Nazaret.

749
00:40:03,340 --> 00:40:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nedzer, odtuda.

750
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zato što grad sam u svome nazivu

751
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] ima aluziju na Izaju 11.

752
00:40:14,719 --> 00:40:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] Zvače se Nazarečevi.

753
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zvače se čovjek granja.

754
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo je to tako reći.

755
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek koji živi u Nazaretu,

756
00:40:21,579 --> 00:40:22,280
[SPEAKER_00] u gradu granja.

757
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u tome je stvar.

758
00:40:23,719 --> 00:40:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] Opet iluzija na ono što je Izaija rekao

759
00:40:26,679 --> 00:40:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] s obzirom na dolazak Mesije.

760
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, čisto da znate,

761
00:40:30,539 --> 00:40:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, ako ste ikad išli tražiti

762
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] da se ispune riječi proroka,

763
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] zvače se Nazarečevi.

764
00:40:35,179 --> 00:40:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] I odite gledati, koji prorok je to rekao?

765
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Zvače se.

766
00:40:37,239 --> 00:40:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nigdje, nema toga nigdje.

767
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] To vam je ova stvar.

768
00:40:41,719 --> 00:40:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, e sada,

769
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] idemo vidjeti Josip nam je u centru.

770
00:40:45,239 --> 00:40:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zdrao mi je sestro,

771
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] vičeras nije toliko Isus,

772
00:40:48,219 --> 00:40:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] nego nam je Josip sad u centru.

773
00:40:49,659 --> 00:40:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] I idemo vidjeti progon Josipove obitelji

774
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] nakon uskrsnuća.

775
00:40:53,380 --> 00:40:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, progon kraljevske obitelji

776
00:40:55,139 --> 00:40:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] nastavlja se i dalje.

777
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je ova važno?

778
00:40:57,239 --> 00:40:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidite koliko su ljudi

779
00:40:58,519 --> 00:40:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] i za vrijeme,

780
00:40:59,679 --> 00:41:01,780
[SPEAKER_00] u Isusovo vrijeme,

781
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] u vrijeme njegova rođenja, života

782
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] i kasnije, nakon njegova uskrsnuća

783
00:41:05,780 --> 00:41:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] bili svjesni postojanja kraljevske loze.

784
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo Rimljani koji su se bojali toga.

785
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] Progon je Josipove obitelji

786
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] nakon uskrsnuća.

787
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, zemljece Zarezki nam opet o tome govori.

788
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon Jakovljeva mučeništva,

789
00:41:19,599 --> 00:41:22,559
[SPEAKER_00] oni od gospodinovih apostole učenika

790
00:41:22,559 --> 00:41:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] našli su se zajedno s onima

791
00:41:24,019 --> 00:41:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] koji su ljudski rečeno

792
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] od gospodinove obitelji.

793
00:41:27,380 --> 00:41:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] I svi se posavjetovaše

794
00:41:29,159 --> 00:41:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] kome bi dali čast

795
00:41:30,219 --> 00:41:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] da naslijedi Jakova.

796
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Jakov je prvi biskup Jeruzalema bio.

797
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:36,219
[SPEAKER_00] I svi jednodušno odlučiše

798
00:41:36,219 --> 00:41:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] da je upravo Šimun,

799
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] sin Kleofe,

800
00:41:38,699 --> 00:41:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] kojega je vanđelja isto spominju.

801
00:41:41,159 --> 00:41:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sijete se Kleofu,

802
00:41:42,340 --> 00:41:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Kleofina.

803
00:41:44,079 --> 00:41:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo,

804
00:41:45,119 --> 00:41:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] to nije njezino Marija Magdalena,

805
00:41:47,739 --> 00:41:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa je Marija Kleofina.

806
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ima dva imena.

807
00:41:49,619 --> 00:41:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nego,

808
00:41:49,940 --> 00:41:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] Marija,

809
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] žena Kleofe.

810
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

811
00:41:53,019 --> 00:41:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] Kleofina žena.

812
00:41:55,500 --> 00:41:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Kleofina.

813
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:58,320
[SPEAKER_00] Kao, ne znam,

814
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ivona Braslavova.

815
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

816
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

817
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nije Marija Kleofina dva imena,

818
00:42:06,699 --> 00:42:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego Marija,

819
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] čiji muž se zove Kleofa.

820
00:42:09,599 --> 00:42:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je Kleofina žena.

821
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

822
00:42:11,860 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] A taj Kleofa je bio,

823
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] sljedeće put ćemo ići podrobnije,

824
00:42:15,659 --> 00:42:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

825
00:42:16,420 --> 00:42:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] Josipovo rodoslovo još podrobnije,

826
00:42:19,019 --> 00:42:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] izvan evanđelja,

827
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kleofa je bio Josipov brat.

828
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] Josipov brat, Kleofa.

829
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Napravit ću schemu,

830
00:42:26,579 --> 00:42:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] navzat ćete prezentaciju,

831
00:42:27,699 --> 00:42:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] pripremi da mogu tu,

832
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

833
00:42:29,599 --> 00:42:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] ok.

834
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:30,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

835
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

836
00:42:31,099 --> 00:42:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] ko onda bio Šimun?

837
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je bio sin Josipova brata,

838
00:42:35,599 --> 00:42:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] Šimun je bio Josipov nečak,

839
00:42:37,079 --> 00:42:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

840
00:42:37,659 --> 00:42:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ovog Josipa o kojem sad pričamo,

841
00:42:40,199 --> 00:42:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je vađelja isto spominju,

842
00:42:42,300 --> 00:42:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] dostojan biskupske stolice u Jeruzalemu.

843
00:42:44,659 --> 00:42:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio,

844
00:42:45,300 --> 00:42:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako se kaže,

845
00:42:46,159 --> 00:42:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] spasitelj jevrođak,

846
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer Kleofa bijaše Josipov brat.

847
00:42:49,380 --> 00:42:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] A Vespazijan,

848
00:42:50,940 --> 00:42:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] rimski car,

849
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:53,719
[SPEAKER_00] nakon opsade Jeruzalema,

850
00:42:53,719 --> 00:42:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] dao je nalog,

851
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] da se pronađu svi koji bi bili iz loze Davidove,

852
00:42:57,519 --> 00:42:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je važno.

853
00:42:58,719 --> 00:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

854
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] rimski carovi su se bojali loze Davidove.

855
00:43:01,219 --> 00:43:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ne bi preostao nitko među žinovima,

856
00:43:03,900 --> 00:43:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi bio iz kraljevske obitelji.

857
00:43:06,380 --> 00:43:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

858
00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] i kasnije dolazi do mučeništva,

859
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] isto tog jadnog Josipova.

860
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nečaka,

861
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] vidite,

862
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] progon Josipove kraljevske obitelji

863
00:43:14,079 --> 00:43:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] se cijelo vrijeme događa

864
00:43:16,559 --> 00:43:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] i događao se

865
00:43:17,260 --> 00:43:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] i želi se zatrti.

866
00:43:18,199 --> 00:43:20,219
[SPEAKER_00] Isto je u zemlji cezarenski,

867
00:43:20,219 --> 00:43:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

868
00:43:20,599 --> 00:43:21,840
[SPEAKER_00] neki od ovih

869
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] obtužiše Šimuna,

870
00:43:23,079 --> 00:43:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] sina Kleofina,

871
00:43:24,199 --> 00:43:26,239
[SPEAKER_00] da potječe iz loze Davidove

872
00:43:26,239 --> 00:43:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] i da je kršćanin.

873
00:43:27,139 --> 00:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pogubna kombinacija.

874
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] E mi je iz loze Davidove,

875
00:43:30,179 --> 00:43:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] evo još kršćanin.

876
00:43:31,019 --> 00:43:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] Super,

877
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] daj ga.

878
00:43:31,739 --> 00:43:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog toga je podnio mučeništvo

879
00:43:34,460 --> 00:43:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] u dobi od 120 godina.

880
00:43:36,500 --> 00:43:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

881
00:43:38,179 --> 00:43:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] nema smisla,

882
00:43:38,900 --> 00:43:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] kojiš,

883
00:43:39,639 --> 00:43:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] 102,

884
00:43:39,980 --> 00:43:40,780
[SPEAKER_00] daj ga pusti.

885
00:43:40,780 --> 00:43:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

886
00:43:44,980 --> 00:43:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] ok.

887
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali eto,

888
00:43:47,739 --> 00:43:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] da slučajno u 120.

889
00:43:49,559 --> 00:43:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi dobio potomka,

890
00:43:51,260 --> 00:43:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] jel da?

891
00:43:51,579 --> 00:43:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

892
00:43:52,559 --> 00:43:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] iako dobro,

893
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] bio je biskup.

894
00:43:54,099 --> 00:43:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

895
00:43:55,599 --> 00:43:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] kada je trajan bio car,

896
00:43:57,579 --> 00:43:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] a Atik Kozul,

897
00:43:58,860 --> 00:43:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] kasnije,

898
00:43:59,500 --> 00:44:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] dok je trajala carska potraga

899
00:44:01,280 --> 00:44:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] za onima koji su iz Davidovske tenastije,

900
00:44:03,559 --> 00:44:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] nogi bijahu isto uhičani

901
00:44:05,300 --> 00:44:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] samo zato jer su potomci

902
00:44:06,920 --> 00:44:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevske obitelji.

903
00:44:09,639 --> 00:44:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego,

904
00:44:11,139 --> 00:44:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] e da,

905
00:44:11,860 --> 00:44:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] e sada,

906
00:44:12,559 --> 00:44:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] zaključit ću,

907
00:44:14,800 --> 00:44:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] prije nego što krenemo na onu našu isto

908
00:44:17,139 --> 00:44:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] problematiku,

909
00:44:20,059 --> 00:44:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] Josip i njegov status,

910
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevski status,

911
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] status među svecima,

912
00:44:25,139 --> 00:44:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

913
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte recimo isto crkveni oci

914
00:44:29,599 --> 00:44:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] kako lijepo kažu,

915
00:44:30,599 --> 00:44:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] isto i tekako svjesni

916
00:44:32,420 --> 00:44:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] Josipove kraljevski časti,

917
00:44:34,820 --> 00:44:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] kralj Tesar,

918
00:44:35,619 --> 00:44:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

919
00:44:35,820 --> 00:44:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] Malo ćemo poetski zaključiti,

920
00:44:37,880 --> 00:44:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] Efrem Sirski,

921
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] crkveni otac,

922
00:44:41,059 --> 00:44:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] istočni naravno jer je Sirski,

923
00:44:42,780 --> 00:44:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] inače ga zovu Harfa Duha Svetoga,

924
00:44:45,139 --> 00:44:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] jer je prekrasno pisao poeziju,

925
00:44:46,860 --> 00:44:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] u svojim božičnim himnima kaže ovo,

926
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je prigrlio i milovao sina

927
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao svoje djete,

928
00:44:55,900 --> 00:44:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] služio mu je kao Bogu,

929
00:44:57,559 --> 00:45:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] radovao se u njemu jer je on jedini dobar

930
00:45:00,440 --> 00:45:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] i klanjao mu se kao pravedome.

931
00:45:02,340 --> 00:45:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Tko me učinio vrijednim takve neizmjene časti

932
00:45:05,260 --> 00:45:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] da sin sve viš njega

933
00:45:06,400 --> 00:45:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] bude ujedno i moj sin.

934
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] David, moj praotac,

935
00:45:09,679 --> 00:45:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] nosio je krunu.

936
00:45:10,960 --> 00:45:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] No meni je uskračena ta čast,

937
00:45:13,119 --> 00:45:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] evo vidite kako je Efrem ovdje

938
00:45:14,480 --> 00:45:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] kaže za Josipa,

939
00:45:16,539 --> 00:45:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] meni kojem je krv određena da kraljuje,

940
00:45:19,039 --> 00:45:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] život je udjelio da budem drvodjelja.

941
00:45:21,320 --> 00:45:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] No kruna koja je oteta,

942
00:45:23,059 --> 00:45:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] sada je vraćena po tebi,

943
00:45:24,599 --> 00:45:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] o kralju svih kraljeva,

944
00:45:25,920 --> 00:45:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] ti koji kraljuješ s prijestolja

945
00:45:28,059 --> 00:45:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] moga naruče.

946
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jako lijepo,

947
00:45:30,360 --> 00:45:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] evo tu je prijestolje

948
00:45:31,780 --> 00:45:33,860
[SPEAKER_00] Isusovos Josipova naruče.

949
00:45:33,860 --> 00:45:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jako lijepo.

950
00:45:34,519 --> 00:45:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kako je Efrem,

951
00:45:35,460 --> 00:45:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako se želite poetski,

952
00:45:38,079 --> 00:45:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] na kršćanski način udvarati nekome,

953
00:45:40,539 --> 00:45:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] citirajte mu Efrema Sirskog.

954
00:45:42,440 --> 00:45:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, dobro.

955
00:45:45,239 --> 00:45:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ponizno svetoga Josipa,

956
00:45:46,480 --> 00:45:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Papa Lav 13.

957
00:45:48,739 --> 00:45:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je Josip kraljevske krvi,

958
00:45:50,760 --> 00:45:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] zadovoljan sa svojim skromnim primanjima,

959
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] podnio kušnje i terete teških životnih previranja,

960
00:45:56,639 --> 00:45:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] i to svojom velikodušnošću,

961
00:45:58,440 --> 00:46:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] u nasljedovodu svoga vlastitog sina,

962
00:46:00,599 --> 00:46:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je uzevši lik sluge,

963
00:46:02,340 --> 00:46:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] premda gospodara života,

964
00:46:03,599 --> 00:46:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] svojevoljno se podredio muci poniženju.

965
00:46:05,840 --> 00:46:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] Što ovo znači?

966
00:46:06,920 --> 00:46:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je snažno.

967
00:46:09,579 --> 00:46:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vi imate Josipov očinstvu kao slici Božjeg očinstva,

968
00:46:14,500 --> 00:46:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] ćemo svakako još podrobnije,

969
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali htio bi ovdje onako malo,

970
00:46:17,559 --> 00:46:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo je diljivo zapravo gledati Isusa Malenog,

971
00:46:21,820 --> 00:46:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji želi nasljedovati,

972
00:46:25,119 --> 00:46:26,699
[SPEAKER_00] ako je li čovjek,

973
00:46:26,699 --> 00:46:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer nije samo Bog,

974
00:46:27,340 --> 00:46:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego i čovjek,

975
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji se ugleda i želi nasljedovati svoga tatu Josipa,

976
00:46:32,500 --> 00:46:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] El Zemaljskog.

977
00:46:33,360 --> 00:46:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] I taj tata je svjesen svoje kraljevske časti,

978
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, sve ovo što sam rekao,

979
00:46:40,280 --> 00:46:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve jedno, dakle,

980
00:46:41,880 --> 00:46:44,639
[SPEAKER_00] u svoje poniznosti slušao je sve,

981
00:46:44,639 --> 00:46:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] nije se bahatio,

982
00:46:45,800 --> 00:46:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] a rekao sam mogao,

983
00:46:47,139 --> 00:46:47,800
[SPEAKER_00] imao je resurse,

984
00:46:47,800 --> 00:46:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] mogao se postaviti i tako dalje.

985
00:46:49,239 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je trenutak,

986
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] kada je Isus na križu,

987
00:46:53,960 --> 00:46:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] i kada mu se rugaju s križa,

988
00:46:56,079 --> 00:46:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] ti li si kralj židovski,

989
00:46:57,579 --> 00:46:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] ajde si iđi s križa,

990
00:46:59,500 --> 00:47:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] pokaži nam i tako dalje.

991
00:47:01,300 --> 00:47:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se vidi Josipova poniznost.

992
00:47:02,860 --> 00:47:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] Kada Isus nije pristal na provokacije,

993
00:47:05,840 --> 00:47:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] dok je na svom prijestolju križa.

994
00:47:08,079 --> 00:47:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti kralj židovski,

995
00:47:10,119 --> 00:47:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] ako si ti spasitelj,

996
00:47:11,440 --> 00:47:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] spasi nas,

997
00:47:12,300 --> 00:47:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] spasi sebe,

998
00:47:12,980 --> 00:47:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] siđi s križa,

999
00:47:13,659 --> 00:47:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] pokaži nam,

1000
00:47:14,219 --> 00:47:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] dokaži nam i tako dalje.

1001
00:47:15,300 --> 00:47:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] Josip se isto mogao dokazati,

1002
00:47:17,139 --> 00:47:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam kralj

1003
00:47:17,880 --> 00:47:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] i pokoriću tebe Herode,

1004
00:47:19,780 --> 00:47:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji prijetiš moju obitelj.

1005
00:47:21,039 --> 00:47:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] Nije.

1006
00:47:21,820 --> 00:47:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja bih rekao

1007
00:47:23,360 --> 00:47:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] da čak taj trenutak na križu,

1008
00:47:25,059 --> 00:47:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] gdje Isus ostaje dostojan,

1009
00:47:27,300 --> 00:47:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] ostaje ponizan,

1010
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to je isto vremeno

1011
00:47:30,199 --> 00:47:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] i ona Josipovska poniznost,

1012
00:47:31,760 --> 00:47:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] koju je gledao čito vrijeme

1013
00:47:33,360 --> 00:47:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] tijekom svoga odrastanja i djetinstva

1014
00:47:35,199 --> 00:47:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] u svome otcu Josipu,

1015
00:47:37,699 --> 00:47:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] možemo to tako reći.

1016
00:47:38,699 --> 00:47:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] Evo je jedna snažna ovdje poveznica

1017
00:47:40,400 --> 00:47:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] koju mogu iščitati iz ovoga

1018
00:47:41,900 --> 00:47:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] što je Papa Lav 13.

1019
00:47:42,920 --> 00:47:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] htio ovdje reći.

1020
00:47:44,539 --> 00:47:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] I na kraju Josip zaista je najveći,

1021
00:47:47,539 --> 00:47:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] veći od Ivana Krstitelja.

1022
00:47:48,900 --> 00:47:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] Iako Isus sam kaže ovo,

1023
00:47:51,639 --> 00:47:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] sve ti sad suprostavljaš Isusu

1024
00:47:54,199 --> 00:47:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovim riječima,

1025
00:47:55,119 --> 00:47:58,320
[SPEAKER_00] što zapravo Isus kaže

1026
00:47:58,320 --> 00:48:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] za situaciju Ivana Krstitelja.

1027
00:48:02,980 --> 00:48:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih da si poredate prioritete.

1028
00:48:05,480 --> 00:48:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] Bog, blažda djevica Marija,

1029
00:48:08,480 --> 00:48:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Josip.

1030
00:48:09,539 --> 00:48:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je eventualno sveti Ivana Krstitelj

1031
00:48:11,139 --> 00:48:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] i drugi sveci.

1032
00:48:12,980 --> 00:48:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] Među rođenima od žene,

1033
00:48:14,219 --> 00:48:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] nitko nije veći od Ivana.

1034
00:48:15,820 --> 00:48:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo reći, pa kako onda može biti

1035
00:48:17,760 --> 00:48:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Josip veći od Ivana?

1036
00:48:19,280 --> 00:48:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] Što kaže dalje?

1037
00:48:21,340 --> 00:48:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] Morate dalje čitati, čitajte kontekst.

1038
00:48:23,739 --> 00:48:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] A ipak, i najmanji u kraljevstvu Božjem

1039
00:48:27,360 --> 00:48:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] veći je od njega.

1040
00:48:28,659 --> 00:48:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, veći od Ivana Krstitelja.

1041
00:48:31,559 --> 00:48:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je Josip najmanji možda

1042
00:48:33,599 --> 00:48:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] u kraljevstvu Božjem,

1043
00:48:34,539 --> 00:48:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] opet je veći od Ivana Krstitelja.

1044
00:48:36,460 --> 00:48:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] S time ću zaključiti.

1045
00:48:38,079 --> 00:48:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] Imate možda kako pitanje.

1046
00:48:41,400 --> 00:48:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] Slušam.

1047
00:48:42,980 --> 00:48:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, hvala Bogu, hvala

1048
00:48:48,039 --> 00:48:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] da niko nema pitanje.

1049
00:48:48,860 --> 00:48:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] A gdje ideš u ruku,

1050
00:48:50,380 --> 00:48:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] poslije ćeš dobiti.

1051
00:48:52,039 --> 00:48:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da, dobro.

1052
00:48:54,539 --> 00:48:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala.

